67	 
68	 ## Stack & architecture
69	 
70	 This is a Next.js 16 App Router template wired to shadcn/ui. It is intentionally minimal — most of the "architecture" is the conventions baked into the tooling config, not custom code.
71	 
72	-- **Next.js 16 + React 19**, App Router under `app/`. `app/layout.tsx` is the root layout and wraps everything in `ThemeProvider`. Dev uses Turbopack.
73	-- **Tailwind CSS v4** via `@tailwindcss/postcss` (see `postcss.config.mjs`). There is **no `tailwind.config.*`** — theme tokens and `@theme` live in `app/globals.css`, which is also what `components.json` and the Prettier plugin point at.
74	-- **shadcn/ui** is configured in `components.json`: style `radix-nova`, RSC on, RTL on, icon library `lucide`, base color `neutral`. Add new components with `npx shadcn@latest add <name>`; they land in `components/ui/`.
75	+- **Next.js 16 + React 19**, App Router under `src/app/`. `src/app/layout.tsx` is the root layout and wraps everything in `ThemeProvider`. Dev uses Turbopack.
76	+- **Tailwind CSS v4** via `@tailwindcss/postcss` (see `postcss.config.mjs`). There is **no `tailwind.config.*`** — theme tokens and `@theme` live in `src/app/globals.css`, which is also what `components.json` points at.
77	+- **shadcn/ui** is configured in `components.json`: style `radix-nova`, RSC on, RTL on, icon library `lucide`, base color `neutral`. Add new components with `npx shadcn@latest add <name>`; they land in `src/components/ui/`.
78	 - **Radix primitives** are imported from the single `radix-ui` package (e.g. `import { Slot } from "radix-ui"`), not `@radix-ui/*` sub-packages. Follow this when adding components.
79	-- **Path aliases** (from `tsconfig.json` + `components.json`): `@/*` → repo root. Canonical aliases are `@/components`, `@/components/ui`, `@/lib`, `@/lib/utils`, `@/hooks`.
80	-- **Styling helper**: `cn()` in `lib/utils.ts` composes `clsx` + `tailwind-merge`. Variants use `class-variance-authority` (`cva`). Both `cn` and `cva` are registered as `tailwindFunctions` in `.prettierrc`, so class strings inside them get sorted by `prettier-plugin-tailwindcss`.
81	-- **Theming**: `components/theme-provider.tsx` wraps `next-themes` (attribute=`class`, default=`system`) and installs a global hotkey — pressing `d` (outside of inputs/contenteditable) toggles light/dark.
82	+- **Path aliases** (from `tsconfig.json` + `components.json`): `@/*` → `src/`. Canonical aliases are `@/components`, `@/components/ui`, `@/lib`, `@/lib/utils`, `@/hooks`.
83	+- **Styling helper**: `cn()` in `src/lib/utils.ts` composes `clsx` + `tailwind-merge`. Variants use `class-variance-authority` (`cva`).
84	+- **Theming**: `src/components/theme-provider.tsx` wraps `next-themes` (attribute=`class`, default=`system`) and installs a global hotkey — pressing `d` (outside of inputs/contenteditable) toggles light/dark.
85	 
86	 ## Code style
87	 
88	-- Prettier: **no semicolons**, double quotes, 2-space tabs, `trailingComma: es5`, `printWidth: 80`, `endOfLine: lf`. Match existing files (e.g. `app/layout.tsx`, `components/ui/button.tsx`).
89	-- TypeScript `strict` is on.
90	+- **Biome**: no semicolons, double quotes, 2-space indentation, `trailingCommas: es5`, `lineWidth: 80`, `lineEnding: lf`. Configured in `biome.json`.
91	+- TypeScript `strict` is on, `noUncheckedIndexedAccess: true`.
92	+- Pre-commit hook (husky + lint-staged) runs `biome check --write --no-errors-on-unmatched --staged` on staged files.
